<h1>about</h1>
<p><a href="https://github.com/tonydng/photo_gallery">This Photo Gallery</a> is a Rails project in version 3.2.13 with <a href="https://github.com/tonydng/photo_gallery/tree/master/spec/features">full integration test</a>. The main idea of this application is that it can let a user to sign up, login, create (read, update, delete) his/her own gallery, and upload photos to this gallery. Also it can let a user to make comments about other people's photos. Beside serving for PC, this website can be viewed from any mobile phones/ipads without spending time to resize the browser window because it is a responsive website.</p>
